These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-6-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola
There 2 different types of food: pepper, banana
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, reading
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, freelancer
1. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
2. the freelancer is not the person eating banana##6
3. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |      2      |
| Beverage   | cola      | mirinda    |
| Food       | banana       | pepper    |
| Hobby      | reading     | filmmaking |
| Job        | journalist | freelancer     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-6-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, family
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, badminton
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, bus
1. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is not the person drinking sprite##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite | juice         |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller      | family |
| Sport         | biathlon      | badminton  |
| Transport     | bus        | skateboard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-6-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, dancing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, epic
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, taxi
1. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person drinking cola##6
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade    | cola        |
| Hobby         | dancing | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | fantasy |
| Transport     | scooter    | taxi |

