.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-6-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, trance
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, colombian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, cricket
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, trike
1. the italian is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
2. the person who's sport is cricket is not the fan trance##6
3. the italian is the fan trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Music-Genre   | techno | trance      |
| Nationality   | colombian      | italian |
| Sport         | cricket     | badminton  |
| Transport     | trike     | boat  |

