.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-6-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, video-games
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, designer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary
2 different pets are kept: bird, frog
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the designer##5
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the owner of the frog##6
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks  | video-games |
| Job           | designer | freelancer  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | martial-arts |
| Pet           | frog     | bird     |

